Card Name: Test Case: User Navigation - Sanity Test
Card Description:
Smoke test, high level test to verify the user can successfully navigate around the site.

Steps:
1- Navigate to http://localhost:3000/
2. click buttons: 
  -See all bots
  -Draw
  -Select 2 bots
  -duel
  -Play again

Postconditions:
-Home page should load with information
-see all bots button should display all bots
-draw button should display 5 random bots
-selecting bots should add them to your duo
-should show computer bots and the duel takes place
-winner should be declared
-should bring you back to the beginning

Card Name: test case add and remove bots
Card Description:
attempt to add and remove different bots before confirming team

expected outcome:

When you click add to duo, it should allow you to add the bot to the duo, and have no more than 2. removing a bot should put it back in your draw pile. adding a different bot should still only allow the max of 2.
